---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const listingURL = 'https://theabacoclub.com/rentals/cabana-112/';

const structuredData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "LodgingBusiness",
      "name": "Cabana 112 at The Abaco Club",
      "description": "A private, freestanding octagonal cabana at The Abaco Club on Winding Bay, Abaco, Bahamas. Steps from two miles of white-sand beach, set along the first fairway of the #1 golf course in the Bahamas.",
      "url": "https://theabacoclub.com/rentals/cabana-112/",
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "addressLocality": "Marsh Harbour",
        "addressRegion": "Abaco",
        "addressCountry": "BS"
      },
      "numberOfRooms": "1",
      "amenityFeature": [
        { "@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Beachfront access", "value": true },
        { "@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Golf course view", "value": true },
        { "@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Full kitchen", "value": true },
        { "@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Rainfall shower", "value": true },
        { "@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Sunroom", "value": true }
      ],
      "priceRange": "$899–$1,100 per night",
      "image": "https://theabacoclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DJI_20241014103859_0246_D.jpg"
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "Cabana 112 Abaco",
      "url": "https://cabana112abaco.com"
    }
  ]
};
---

<Base
  title="Private Cabana Rental in the Bahamas"
  description="Cabana 112 at The Abaco Club — a serene one-bedroom private retreat on Winding Bay, Abaco. Steps from 2 miles of white-sand beach, with golf course views and a spa-style rainfall shower."
  canonicalURL="/"
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <style>
    .hero {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero .eyebrow {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--coral);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.2;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--coral);
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero .btn:hover { background: #e0705f; color: #fff; }

    .hero .meta {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .features {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature h2 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .feature .icon {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 0 1.5rem; }

    .narrative {
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .narrative h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .narrative p {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .narrative .booking-prompt {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--teal);
    }

    .narrative .booking-prompt p {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .narrative .booking-prompt a.btn-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid var(--navy);
      color: var(--navy);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .narrative .booking-prompt a.btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .specs {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .specs h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    }

    .specs-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem 3rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .spec-item .value {
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--coral);
    }

    .spec-item .label {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .blog-cta {
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .blog-cta h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .blog-cta p {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .blog-cta a { font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 0.88rem; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Abaco, Bahamas · The Abaco Club on Winding Bay</p>
    <h1>A Private Cabana on the Bahamas' Finest Beach</h1>
    <p>
      Cabana 112 is a freestanding one-bedroom retreat tucked between the first fairway
      and two miles of uninterrupted white-sand shoreline. Quiet, private, and entirely yours.
    </p>
    <a href={listingURL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">
      View Booking Details at The Abaco Club
    </a>
    <p class="meta">1 Bedroom · 1 Bathroom · Sleeps 2+ · 570 sq ft · $899–$1,100/night</p>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">🏖</span>
      <h2>Two miles of private beach</h2>
      <p>Winding Bay is consistently ranked among the most beautiful stretches of sand in the Atlantic. Cabana 112 is just steps away.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">⛳</span>
      <h2>Golf course setting</h2>
      <p>The cabana sits directly on the first fairway of the #1-ranked golf course in the Bahamas. The sunroom looks right out over the green.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">🚿</span>
      <h2>Spa-style rainfall shower</h2>
      <p>After a day on the beach, come home to a spa-like bathroom with an oversized rainfall shower — recently renovated to feel like a boutique hotel.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">🍳</span>
      <h2>Full gourmet kitchen</h2>
      <p>Oven, stovetop, microwave, fridge, and freezer. A breakfast bar for three, perfect for morning coffee before an early tee time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">🌊</span>
      <h2>Club amenities included</h2>
      <p>Quick access to Flipper's Beach Bar, tennis and pickleball courts, the golf shop, and the first tee — all within a short walk.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="icon">🏡</span>
      <h2>Octagonal architecture</h2>
      <p>The cabana's unique shape creates a spacious, airy feel. High ceilings in the living room let the trade wind breezes do their thing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <section class="narrative">
    <h2>What makes Cabana 112 different</h2>
    <p>
      Most rental properties at The Abaco Club are larger homes suited for families or groups.
      Cabana 112 is the rare exception: a compact, deeply private space that feels more like a
      luxury boutique suite than a vacation rental. The octagonal footprint, the way morning
      light moves through the sunroom, the sound of golf carts on the path outside — it
      has its own distinct character.
    </p>
    <p>
      The cabana sits on the first fairway, which means you're surrounded by manicured grass
      and tropical foliage rather than being at the edge of a road or parking area. At the
      same time, the beach is genuinely close — a short walk through the club grounds puts
      you on Winding Bay, one of the most photographed stretches of shoreline in the Bahamas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Rentals at The Abaco Club are restricted to members of the Southworth portfolio,
      so the property never feels crowded. If you're already a member of a Southworth club,
      you're already eligible.
    </p>

    <div class="booking-prompt">
      <p>
        Cabana 112 books through The Abaco Club's official reservation system.
        All availability, pricing, and membership eligibility questions are handled there.
      </p>
      <a href={listingURL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-outline">
        View Official Listing &amp; Availability →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs">
    <h2>At a glance</h2>
    <div class="specs-grid">
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">1 BR</div>
        <div class="label">Bedroom</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">570</div>
        <div class="label">Square feet</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">2+</div>
        <div class="label">Guests</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">$899</div>
        <div class="label">Starting per night</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">#1</div>
        <div class="label">Golf in Bahamas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-item">
        <div class="value">2 mi</div>
        <div class="label">Private beach</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-cta">
    <h2>From the owner's journal</h2>
    <p>
      I write occasionally about life at the cabana — renovations, what to pack for Abaco,
      the best time of year to visit, and what it's actually like to spend time at Winding Bay.
    </p>
    <a href="/blog/">Read the journal →</a>
  </section>
</Base>
